Step 1: Create a student list
Step 2: Ask user to insert students' name into the student list
Step 3: Asking user what the user want to do to the student list
1) Delete student
2) Add new student
3) Modify a student's name
4) Display the student list
Step 4: Repeat step 3 until user choose to end
Step 5: Add validation to every process
1) Delete or modify student's name only when it is available
2) Show error when there are no student name to be displayed

Advanced:
Step 6: Create a txt file to store the student name list
